name: Jay Slater missing Tenerife
summary: The disappearance of British teenager Jay Slater in Tenerife continues to be a major concern. His mother has expressed concern that police have not made sufficient efforts in the search and has drawn a comparison to her own daughter's disappearance. Slater's father has described the situation as a "living hell." Despite a week-long search, Slater's whereabouts remain unknown. Authorities are focusing their efforts on ravines and a village and valley, and have shared photographs of the property where he was last seen.
